### AI usage
AI tools were used as assistant support for:
- Clarifying edge cases in parsing/execution behavior
- Reviewing and explaining Valgrind output
- Suggesting debugging workflow and leak-check commands

All implementation choices, integration, and final validation were performed and verified in this project codebase.
